✅ Correct:
```jsx
function useFriendStatus(friendID) {
  const [isOnline, setIsOnline] = useState(null);
  // ...
}
```

❌ Incorrect:
```jsx
function getFriendStatus(friendID) {
  const [isOnline, setIsOnline] = useState(null); // Error!
}
```

Functions not starting with `use` cannot call hooks.
